.TH MNEMOSYNE-WIKI-STATUS 1 "2026-06-23" "mnemosyne" "Mnemosyne CLI"
.SH NAME
mnemosyne wiki-status \- Show read\-only wiki health summary.
.SH SYNOPSIS
\fBmnemosyne wiki-status\fR [options]
.SH DESCRIPTION
Show read\-only wiki health summary.
.SH OPTIONS
.TP
\fB\-\-wiki\-root\fR
LLM Wiki root (default: ~/mnemosyne/wiki)
.TP
\fB\-\-db\-path\fR
KnowledgeGraph DB path
.TP
\fB\-\-format\fR
.TP
\fB\-\-lock\-timeout\fR
Seconds to wait for the wiki write lock on write commands
.SH SEE ALSO
mnemosyne(1)
